Enugu- born Nollywood actress and producer, Uche Ogbodo is pregnant with her second child. The actress had recounted walking out of her marriage 10 months after in 2013 and how she had never envisaged being a single mother. She got married to her ex-husband, Apo Arthur in 2013 with whom she welcomed a baby girl in 2014. The Norway-based is an ex footballer. The actress took to her Instagram page on March 12, 2021 to share photos of herself wearing a new look and displaying her baby bump. She wrote: “Flying private with my bunny, In the Oven, NAh ! You can’t seat with Us, 3 is a Crowd”. 